Page will reload'=>'設定已成功匯入。頁面會重新載入。','Could not read the options from the provided JSON file'=>'無法從目前的 JSON 檔案讀取選項設定。','The provided file is not a JSON file.'=>'目前的檔案不是 JSON 檔案。','The provided file is not a JSON'=>'目前的檔案不是 JSON 檔案。','Only administrator can import settings'=>'僅有網站管理員可以匯入設定。','Remote file could not be reached'=>'無法連接至遠端檔案。','Font remain visible during load'=>'載入字型時，字型仍會繼續顯示','Apply "noopener noreferrer" to links which have target"_blank" attribute and the anchor leads to external websites'=>'將 noopener noreferrer 屬性值套用至包含 target="_blank" 屬性值的連結及導向外部網站的錨點','Cross-origin Safe Links'=>'跨站安全連結','Please clear Varnish after applying the new settings.'=>'套用新設定後，請清除 Varnish 快取。','More info here'=>'進一步了解相關資訊','You can add specific keywords to identify the inline JavaScript to be delayed. Each script identifying keyword must be added on a new line.'=>'網站管理員可以新增指定關鍵字以辨別要延遲載入的內嵌 JavaScript。請一行輸入一個能辨別指令碼的關鍵字。','Delay JS Inline Scripts'=>'延遲內嵌 JS 指令碼','Enter Font/CSS URL...'=>'請輸入字型/CSS 網址...','This feature is supported by Chromium based browsers (Chrome, Opera, Microsoft Edge Chromimum, Brave...);'=>'以 Chromium 引擎開發的瀏覽器，才支援這項功能。例如: Chrome、Opera、Microsoft Edge Chromium 及 Brave 等。','When users hover over links, the cache is created in advance. The page will load faster upon link visiting.'=>'使用者游標於連結暫留後，便會提前建立快取，這會讓使用者點擊連結後載入頁面更加快速。','Preload Links'=>'預先載入連結','Enable native browser lazy load'=>'啟用瀏覽器原生延遲載入功能','This option requires the library PHP DOMDocument and PHP DOMXPath'=>'這項功能需要 PHP 的 DOMDocument 及 DOMXPath 函式庫。','Images will begin to load before being displayed on screen.'=>'圖片會在顯示於檢視區前開始載入。','Lazy Load Images'=>'圖片延遲載入','- You can leave the option enabled and identify which line found in the textarea is causing the issue, then remove only that online that line.'=>'- 啟用設定後，在文字區域中識別是哪一行造成問題，然後移除造成問題的那一行。','- You can disable the option altogether.'=>'- 完全停用這項設定。','If JavaScript errors show up in front-end you can try the following solutions.'=>'如果網站前端顯示 JavaScript 錯誤，網站管理員可以試著使用以下解決方案。','Delay inline JavaScript issue'=>'延遲內嵌 JavaScript 的相關問題','is not a valid CDN url.'=>'是無效的 CDN 網址。','This option might not work properly with some page builders.'=>'某些頁面編輯器會造成這項功能無法正確執行。','Enable cache for WP standard user roles: Administrator, Editor, Author, Contributor.'=>'為 WordPress 標準使用者角色啟用快取: 網站管理員、編輯、作者、投稿者、訂閱者。','Deactivate'=>'停用','We recommend deactivating these plugin(s) and installing a compatible version.'=>'建議停用這些外掛並安裝相容版本。','The following plugin(s) is not compatible with Breeze and could conflict with plugin options.'=>'以下外掛與 Breeze 不相容，並且會造成快取外掛設定衝突。','Breeze Incompatible Plugins'=>'與 Breeze 不相容的外掛','Network Only - deactivate from Network'=>'僅多站網路: 於多站網路中停用','Network Active - deactivate from Network'=>'多站網路啟用: 於多站網路中停用','is not compatible'=>'與 Breeze 不相容。','Plugin'=>'外掛','Purge Site Cache'=>'清除網站快取','This option allows subsite to have different settings/configuration from the network level. Use this option only if you wish to have separate settings for this subsite.'=>'啟用這項設定後，便能在多站網路中為個別子網站進行不同的設定/組態。僅有子網站需要不同設定時，才需要啟用這項設定。','This option allows the subsite to inherit all the cache settings from network. To modify/update the settings please go to network site.'=>'啟用這項設定後，全部子網站便會套用多站網路層級的全部快取設定。如需修改/變更設定，請前往多站網路主要網站。','Enabling/disabling %s for subsites is only available for Apache 2.4 and above. For lower versions, the Network-level settings will apply.'=>'僅有使用 Apache 2.4 或更新版本的多站網路，才能為個別子網站啟用/停用 [%s] 功能。如果使用舊版 Apache，僅能直接套用多站網路層級設定。','One (or more) URL is incorrect. Please confirm that all URLs have the .js extension'=>'一或多個網址不正確。請確認全部網址結尾均包含 .js 副檔名。','One (or more) URL is invalid. Please check and correct the entry.'=>'一或多個網址無效。請檢查並修正無效的項目。','One (or more) URL is incorrect. Please confirm that all URLs have the .css extension'=>'一或多個網址不正確。請確認全部網址結尾均包含 .css 副檔名。','Does Breeze plugin work with Visual Builder?'=>'Breeze 是否能與各款視覺化編輯器一起執行？','How can I test and verify the results?'=>'如何測試及驗證 Breeze 的快取效果？','Include Inline CSS'=>'包含內嵌 CSS','Include Inline JS'=>'包含內嵌 JS','JS Files With Deferred Loading'=>'延遲載入 JS 檔案','You should add the URL of original files as URL of minified files are not supported.'=>'這個外掛不支援已進行最小化/壓縮處理的 JS 檔案，請輸入原始 JS 檔案的網址。','Enter the complete URLs of JS files to be moved to the footer during minification process.'=>'進行最小化/壓縮處理時，輸入在此的 JS 檔案完整網址會移至頁尾。','Add URL'=>'新增網址','Remove'=>'移除','Enter URL...'=>'請輸入網址...','Move JS Files to Footer'=>'將 JS 檔案移至頁尾','Save Changes'=>'儲存設定','Optimize'=>'最佳化','KnowledgeBase article for details.'=>'這份知識庫文章以取得詳細資訊。','Breeze handles all WordPress multisite instances globally. All the settings for multisite are now handled on the network level.'=>'Breeze 統一處理全部 WordPress 多站網路中全部網站的快取。全部針對多站網路的設定，均屬於多站網路管理員層級。','How does Breeze handle WordPress multisite?'=>'Breeze 如何處理 WordPress 多站網路的快取？','Using Gzip, Breeze compresses the request files, further reducing the size of the download files and speeding up the user experience.'=>'啟用 Gzip 功能後，Breeze 便能壓縮使用者要求的檔案、進一步減少下載檔案的大小，藉以加速以提昇使用者體驗。','How Breeze cache uses Gzip?'=>'Breeze 如何運用 Gzip 功能？','Yes. The process of setting up CloudFlare with Breeze is easy. Check out the following '=>'可以。要讓 Cloudflare 與 Breeze 一起執行的設定程序相當簡單，請參閱','Does Breeze Work With CloudFlare?'=>'Breeze 是否能與 Cloudflare 一起執行？','No, Breeze does not support Push CDN. However, you could use Breeze with Push CDNs using third party plugins.'=>'否，Breeze 不支援主動式 CDN，但這個網站可以使用第三方外掛讓 Breeze 與主動式 CDN 同時執行。','Does Breeze support Push CDN?'=>'Breeze 是否支援主動式 CDN？','Amazon Cloudfront'=>'Amazon Cloudfront','KeyCDN'=>'KeyCDN','MaxCDN'=>'MaxCDN','Breeze supports the following three popular CDNs:'=>'Breeze 支援下列 3 個熱門的 CDN:','What popular CDN are supported by Breeze Plugin?'=>'Breeze 支援哪些熱門的 CDN？','Yes, Breeze Plugin is compatible with Visual Builder.'=>'是的，Breeze 相容於各款視覺化編輯器。','Pingdom'=>'Pingdom','WebPagetest'=>'WebPagetest','Google Page Speed'=>'Google Page Speed','You will be able to see the impact of the Breeze Cache Plugin almost immediately. We also recommend using the following tools for generating metrics:'=>'使用者可以近乎即時的觀察到 Breeze 快取外掛對網站的加速效果，我們也建議使用下列工具產生指標報告藉以評估成效:','You can get your questions answered on the WordPress support forums. If you are a Cloudways customer, please feel free to start a discussion at'=>'使用者可以在 WordPress 技術支援論壇上提出問題並得到回覆。如果是 Cloudways 的客戶，隨時可以在官方討論區進行討論，也就是 ','Where can I get support for Breeze?'=>'在何處可以取得 Breeze 外掛的技術支援？','Breeze has been tested to work with all major hosting providers. In addition, major Breeze options such as Gzip, browser cache, minification, grouping, database optimization. CDN integration will work as expected on all hosting providers.'=>'Breeze 在主要的主機服務提供商都進行過測試。此外，Breeze 的主要功能如 Gzip、瀏覽器快取、檔案最小化、合併檔案、資料庫最佳化及 CDN 整合，在全部主機均能正常執行。','Does it work with all hosting providers?'=>'Breeze 可以執行於各家主機服務提供商的主機嗎？','this KB to exclude URLs from the Varnish cache.'=>'這篇知識庫文章以了解如何從 Varnish 快取機制中排除特定網址內容。','If Varnish is active, you will need to exclude URLs and file type(s) in the Varnish configuration. If you are hosting WordPress websites on Cloudways servers, follow '=>'Varnish 啟用後，便需要在 Varnish 設定中將網址及檔案類型加以排除。如果這個 WordPress 網站代管於 Cloudways 提供的伺服器，請參閱','Can I exclude URLs of individual files and pages from cache?'=>'是否能從快取中排除個別檔案及頁面的網址？','Comments will appear upon moderation as per the comment system (or policy) set in place by the blog owner. Other dynamic changes such as any modifications in files will require a full cache purge.'=>'留言能否即時顯示，會依照網站管理員對留言系統的設定或稽核原則而定；而對動態內容所進行的變更，則必須進行完整的快取清除操作後才能顯示。','Will comments and other dynamic parts of my blog appear immediately?'=>'啟用 Breeze 快取外掛後，網站上的留言及其他動態產生的內容會即時顯示嗎？','Breeze\'s database optimization cleans out unwanted information in a single click.'=>'Breeze 的資料庫最佳化功能，能夠讓網站管理員一鍵清除全部不必要的資料。','WordPress databases are notorious for storing information like post revisions, spam comments and much more. Over time, databases l become bloated and it is a good practice to clear out unwanted information to reduce database size and improve optimization.'=>'眾所周知，WordPress 資料庫儲存了文章內容修訂以及垃圾留言等資訊。網站經營一段時間之後，資料庫便會變的臃腫龐大；定期清除資料庫中不需要的資訊，是減少資料庫大小及增進最佳化的最佳方式。','What does Breeze\'s Database Optimization feature do?'=>'Breeze 的資料庫最佳化功能作用為何？','Breeze supports CDN integration. It allows all static assets (such as images, CSS and JS files) to be served via CDN.'=>'Breeze 支援 CDN 整合，整合後便可由 CDN 處理它所產出的全部靜態檔案，如圖片、CSS 以及 JS 檔。','Does Breeze support CDN?'=>'Breeze 是否支援 CDN？','Does Breeze have compatibility issues with other known plugins?'=>'Breeze 是否與其他外掛有相容性問題？','Breeze does not require any special configuration to work with HTTP or HTTPS pages.'=>'Breeze 無須任何特殊設定，便能同時處理 HTTP 與 HTTPS 頁面。','Is Breeze compatible with HTTPS?'=>'Breeze 是否與 HTTPS 相容？','We strongly recommend that you use Breeze as the only cache plugin for your website. If there are any other cache plugins installed, please ensure that you have disabled them prior to proceeding with the Breeze installation.'=>'我們強烈建議在網站上使用 Breeze，將它作為唯一的快取外掛。如果網站上使用了其他快取外掛，請確保在安裝 Breeze 前已將其停用。','We DO NOT recommend using two WordPress cache plugins at the same time on any WordPress website.'=>'我們並不建議在任何 WordPress 網站上同時使用兩個快取外掛。','Is Breeze compatible with other WordPress Cache plugins?'=>'Breeze 是否與其他 WordPress 快取外掛相容？','Breeze is fully compatible with WordPress Multisite without the need for any extra configuration.'=>'Breeze 與 WordPress 多站網路功能完全相容，且無須進行任何額外設定。','Does Breeze support WordPress Multisite?'=>'Breeze 是否支援 WordPress 多站網路功能？','Breeze is fully compatible with WooCommerce, out of the box. It does not require any special configurations.'=>'Breeze 與 WooCommerce 完全相容，安裝啟用後即可開始執行，且無須進行任何特殊設定。','Does Breeze support WooCommerce?'=>'Breeze 是否支援 WooCommerce？','Breeze, by default, supports Varnish. It has been tested to be fully compatible with Cloudways Servers that come with Varnish pre-installed. If you are using hosting providers other than Cloudways, we suggest you confirm Varnish support with your hosting provider.'=>'Breeze 預設支援 Varnish，且完全相容於 Cloudways 已預先安裝 Varnish 的伺服器。如果目前使用的主機並非由 Cloudways 所提供，建議向網站主機代管服務提供商洽詢關於 Varnish 的支援。','Does Breeze support Varnish and to what extent?'=>'Breeze 是否支援 Varnish？支援到哪個程度？','FAQs'=>'常見問題集','CDN CNAME'=>'CDN CNAME','Delete expired and active transients from the WordPress database.'=>'從資料庫刪除到期及使用中的選項暫存資料。','Backup your database before using the following options!'=>'在執行下列功能前，請先備份網站資料庫！',' article.'=>'文章。','Knowledge Base'=>'知識庫','Add the URLs of the pages (one per line) you wish to exclude from the WordPress internal cache. To exclude URLs from the Varnish cache, please refer to this '=>'以每行一個的方式加入需要予以排除的 WordPress 內部快取頁面網址。如需排除 Varnish 快取網址，請參閱這篇','Cloudways Community Forum.'=>'Cloudways 社群論壇。','VARNISH'=>'VARNISH','ADVANCED OPTIONS'=>'進階設定','BASIC OPTIONS'=>'基本設定','Cache data has been purged: '=>'快取資料已清除: ','Purge Internal Cache'=>'清除內部快取','Hide message'=>'隱藏訊息','Thanks for installing Breeze. It is always recommended not to use more than one caching plugin at the same time. We recommend you to purge cache if necessary.'=>'感謝採用 Breeze。強烈建議不要同時使用多個快取外掛，如有需要，建議清除快取即可。','https://www.cloudways.com'=>'https://www.cloudways.com','Cloudways'=>'Cloudways','Breeze is a cache plugin with extensive options to speed up your website. All the options including Varnish Cache are compatible with Cloudways hosting.'=>'Breeze 是一款具有詳盡設定，可為網站進行加速的快取外掛，同時也提供與 Cloudways 主機代管服務相容的 Varnish 快取設定。','Use this option to instantly Purge Varnish Cache on entire website.'=>'使用這項功能便能立即清除整個網站上的 Varnish 快取。','Purge'=>'清除','Purge Varnish Cache'=>'清除 Varnish 快取','Keep this default if you are a Cloudways customer. Otherwise ask your hosting provider on what to set here.'=>'請注意，如果是 Cloudways 的使用者，請將這項設定維持預設值。如果不是，請向對應的主機代管服務提供商洽詢設定方式。','Varnish Server'=>'Varnish 伺服器','Seems Varnish is disabled on your Application. Please refer to this'=>'Varnish 在伺服器的應用程式中遭到停用。請參閱這篇','Keep this option enabled to automatically purge Varnish cache on actions like publishing new blog posts, pages and comments.'=>'啟用這項設定便會自動清除 Varnish 快取，例如在發佈新文章、頁面及留言後自動清除快取。','Auto Purge Varnish'=>'自動清除 Varnish 快取','By default Varnish is enabled on all WordPress websites hosted on Cloudways.'=>'預設情況下，全部托管於 Cloudways 的 WordPress 網站均已啟用 Varnish。','Post Revisions'=>'文章內容修訂','Keep this option enabled. Use this option to enable relative path for your CDN on your WordPress site.'=>'使用這項功能便能為這個 WordPress 網站上的 CDN 內容分流啟用相對路徑 (請保持啟用這項功能)。','Relative Path'=>'相對路徑','Exclude file types or directories from CDN. Example, enter .css to exclude the CSS files.'=>'排除無需進行 CDN 內容分流的檔案類型或目錄。舉例來說，輸入 .css 便會在進行 CDN 內容分流時排除 CSS 檔案。如需輸入多個項目，請以逗號進行分隔。','Exclude Content'=>'排除內容','Enter the directories (comma separated) of which you want the CDN to serve the content.'=>'請輸入需要進行 CDN 內容分流的目錄。如需輸入多個目錄，請以逗號進行分隔。','CDN Content'=>'CDN 內容','Use double slash \'//\' at the start of CDN CNAME, if you have some pages on  HTTP and some are on HTTPS.'=>'如果這個網站包含 HTTP 及 HTTPS 兩種頁面，在輸入 CDN 主機 CNAME 時僅需輸入雙斜線 //，而無須輸入 HTTP 或 HTTPS。','https://www.domain.com'=>'https://www.domain.com','Enable to make CDN effective on your website.'=>'為這個網站啟用 CDN 功能。','Activate CDN'=>'啟用 CDN','Mobile Cache'=>'行動版網站快取','Enable this to add expires headers to static files. This will ask browsers to either request a file from server or fetch from the browser\'s cache.'=>'啟用這項設定便能為靜態檔案加入到期標頭。這將讓瀏覽器決定從伺服器或從瀏覽器快取要求檔案。','Browser Cache'=>'瀏覽器快取','Enable this to compress your files making HTTP requests fewer and faster.'=>'啟用這項設定便能將傳輸至使用者瀏覽器的檔案進行壓縮，使 HTTP 要求數更少且傳輸速度更快。','Gzip Compression'=>'Gzip 壓縮','Automatically purge internal cache after X minutes. By default this is set to 1440 minutes (1 day)'=>'在指定時間間隔後自動清除內部快取，預設值為 1440 分鐘 (即 1 天)。','Purge Cache After'=>'清除快取時間間隔','This is the basic cache that we recommend should be kept enabled in all cases. Basic cache will build the internal and static caches for the WordPress websites.'=>'這是在全部情況下都應該啟用的基本快取功能。基本快取功能能為 WordPress 網站建立內部快取及靜態快取。','Cache System'=>'快取系統','Use this option to exclude JS files from Minification and Grouping. Enter the URLs of JS files on each line.'=>'使用這項功能便會將指定的 JS 檔案從 [最小化] 及 [合併檔案] 這兩項功能中排除。請以每行一個的方式輸入 JS 檔案網址。','Exclude JS'=>'排除 JS','Use this option to exclude CSS files from Minification and Grouping. Enter the URLs of CSS files on each line.'=>'使用這項功能便會將指定的 CSS 檔案從 [最小化] 及 [合併檔案] 這兩項功能中排除。請以每行一個的方式輸入 CSS 檔案網址。','Exclude CSS'=>'排除 CSS','Varnish'=>'Varnish','CDN'=>'CDN',' Kb static cache cleaned'=>'Kb 靜態快取已清理。','Cloudways Varnish Purge Interval'=>'Cloudways Varnish 清除間隔','Support'=>'技術支援','Settings'=>'設定','Purge Modules'=>'清除模組','Purge All Cache'=>'清除全部快取','Breeze'=>'Breeze']];